      "span_text": "The chemical instability of resveratrol was improved by liposome encapsulation, preventing the inactivation of cis-trans isomerization, and its intravenous administration inhibited tumor growth by approximately 70 % in a murine tumor model, showing that simple solubilization can have important therapeutic benefits  ."
